[2026-04-03T11:11:39+01:00] User reported: firework colour is not changing

Root cause found: particles.Color was defined as int32 but tcell.Color is uint64. 
The conversion truncated the color values (e.g., tcell.ColorRed=0x100000009 became 0x09),
causing all fireworks to render with incorrect/same colors.

Fix: Changed particles.Color from int32 to int64 in pkg/particles/particles.go

